dascandy — 6:31 AM
testing is the investment you can make now that pays of 50x in the future. Test the things that would make debugging really hard, cause impossible bugs or would create lots of impact, and that are relatively easy to test. Then, while developing, create a regression test set of things that failed once and add to it for each bug (as Kovarex demonstrated) how you reproduce it.


